{"_id":"yFIo3lYBPfN46hYU","name":"Brutal Might","type":"feature","img":"icons/creatures/abilities/bear-roar-bite-brown-green.webp","data":{"ability":"","actionOptions":[],"activation":{"cost":"","type":"","reactionTrigger":""},"attack":{"bonus":"","critThreshold":20,"type":""},"area":{"shape":"","size":""},"check":{"ability":"str"},"damage":[],"description":"<p>Gain an expertise die in attempts to grapple and proficiency in improvised weapons. Upon successfully grappling up to two creatures, one or more Size categories smaller than you, you may use them as improvised weapons. You do damage based upon the Size category of the grappled creature and whether you are using the creature(s) one handed or two handed. The creature used in this way also receives damage equal to the amount and type dealt. The creature is considered to be sharing your space whilst being wielded in this way until it escapes your grapple, or dies, and is then moved to a space adjacent to you of its choice.</p><blockquote><h3><strong>What if I have a Small creature in one hand and a Tiny creature in the other, and I smack them together?</strong></h3><p>Nothing could be simpler! You follow the rules for two-weapon fighting in the AG, pg 446. With one hand you swing one creature making your normal roll to hit (being grappled does not change the AC of any of the creatures involved) and then roll damage consulting the relevant part of the table. When using your off hand, the attack roll is the same, but you simply do not add your Strength modifier (unless you have the two-weapon fighting fighting style).</p></blockquote>","duration":{"unit":"","value":""},"healing":[],"proficient":true,"range":[],"save":{"dc":"","onSave":"","targetAbility":""},"source":"","target":{"quantity":"","type":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"featureType":"heritage"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wdmZ3THk4XlklgMo":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.p1hdDOiZHTrGfKHp"}}}
{"_id":"LIwRIBIOBTagEkFU","name":"Constricting Grasp","type":"feature","img":"icons/creatures/reptiles/serpent-horned-green.webp","data":{"ability":"","actionOptions":[],"activation":{"cost":"","type":"","reactionTrigger":""},"attack":{"bonus":"","critThreshold":20,"type":""},"area":{"shape":"","size":""},"check":{"ability":"str"},"damage":[],"description":"<p>You gain the ability to make an attack with the lower half of your body. This is a mel√©e attack that you are proficient in and causes 1d8 + Str modifier bludgeoning damage. If it hits, and your target is up to one Size category larger than you, the target must pass a Strength saving throw versus your maneuver DC or be restrained. You may not use this ability on another target without ending your grapple first. The target must use an action and pass a Strength saving throw versus your maneuver DC to escape your grasp.</p>","duration":{"unit":"","value":""},"healing":[],"proficient":true,"range":[],"save":{"dc":"","onSave":"","targetAbility":""},"source":"","target":{"quantity":"","type":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"featureType":"heritage"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wdmZ3THk4XlklgMo":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.rsC9ASoiPZyRu3mt"}}}
{"_id":"BAhuvc6d09qLGOaz","name":"Fairy Dust","type":"feature","img":"icons/creatures/magical/fae-fairy-winged-glowing-green.webp","data":{"ability":"","actionOptions":[],"activation":{"cost":"","type":"","reactionTrigger":""},"attack":{"bonus":"","critThreshold":20,"type":""},"area":{"shape":"","size":""},"check":{"ability":"str"},"damage":[],"description":"<p>As an action you may move up to your base movement Speed and sprinkle fairy dust onto up to three Medium or smaller creatures. These creatures gain a fly Speed of 30ft for up to 10 minutes. You must take a long rest before using this feature again.</p>","duration":{"unit":"","value":""},"healing":[],"proficient":true,"range":[],"save":{"dc":"","onSave":"","targetAbility":""},"source":"","target":{"quantity":"","type":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"featureType":"heritage"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wdmZ3THk4XlklgMo":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.yENHNPA99BXjKMD4"}}}
{"_id":"sYMiHrs2F1sK394S","name":"Heart-Stopping Shriek","type":"feature","img":"icons/magic/sonic/scream-wail-shout-teal.webp","data":{"ability":"","actionOptions":[],"activation":{"cost":"","type":"","reactionTrigger":""},"attack":{"bonus":"","critThreshold":20,"type":""},"area":{"shape":"","size":""},"check":{"ability":"str"},"damage":[],"description":"<p>Once per short rest, you may let out a mighty roar that causes all creatures of your choice, capable of being stunned, within 30 feet of you, to make Wisdom saving throws vs a DC of 10 + your Constitution modifier + your proficiency bonus or be Stunned.</p>","duration":{"unit":"","value":""},"healing":[],"proficient":true,"range":[],"save":{"dc":"","onSave":"","targetAbility":""},"source":"","target":{"quantity":"","type":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"shortRest"},"featureType":"heritage"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wdmZ3THk4XlklgMo":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.sYMiHrs2F1sK394S"}}}
{"_id":"H75rEj7YABNRnIog","name":"Power of Belief","type":"feature","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-green.webp","data":{"ability":"","actionOptions":[],"activation":{"cost":"","type":"","reactionTrigger":""},"attack":{"bonus":"","critThreshold":20,"type":""},"area":{"shape":"","size":""},"check":{"ability":"str"},"damage":[],"description":"<p>If you fall to zero hit points then, as a reaction, all allies within 30 feet can choose to declare their belief in you. If all allies do this then you instead fall to 1 hit point and may immediately take a turn out of order in the initiative. If all your allies within 30 feet do not have a reaction to spend or do not choose to declare their belief in you then you do not gain use of this power. You may only call upon this power once per long rest.</p>","duration":{"unit":"","value":""},"healing":[],"proficient":true,"range":[],"save":{"dc":"","onSave":"","targetAbility":""},"source":"","target":{"quantity":"","type":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"longRest"},"featureType":"heritage"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"wdmZ3THk4XlklgMo":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.H75rEj7YABNRnIog"}}}
